properties.areaDesc: Coastal Waters from Pigeon Point to Point Pinos California out to 10 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 23 at 2:00PM PST until January 25 at 3:00PM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Seas 8 to 12 feet at 17 seconds expected.

* WHERE...Coastal Waters from Pigeon Point to Point Pinos
California out to 10 nm.

* WHEN...From 9 PM Friday to 3 PM PST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 PM FRIDAY TO 3 PM PST SATURDAY
